sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Istio Gateway /<br/>Gateway API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant VS as VirtualService /<br/>HTTPRoute
    participant PredSvc as Predictor Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Pod as Model Server Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant OAuth as OAuth/kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure/HF)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant StorageInit as storage-initializer<br/>(Init Container)
    participant RouterPod as inference-router<br/>8080/TCP
    participant ISVC_N as InferenceService N<br/>(Graph Step)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,Pod: Flow 1: Standard InferenceService Request
        Client->>GW: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, Bearer token (optional)
        GW->>VS: Route via VirtualService/HTTPRoute<br/>HTTP (mesh internal)
        VS->>PredSvc: Forward to Predictor Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP
        PredSvc->>Pod: Proxy to Model Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        Pod-->>PredSvc: Prediction Response
        PredSvc-->>GW: Response
        GW-->>Client: JSON Response (HTTPS)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 238)
        Note over Client,K8sAPI: Flow 2: InferenceService with OAuth Proxy (ODH)
        Client->>OAuth: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS, Bearer token
        OAuth->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>OAuth: Authorized
        OAuth->>Pod: Forward to Model Server (localhost)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (loopback)
        Pod-->>OAuth: Prediction Response
        OAuth-->>Client: JSON Response (HTTPS)
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Note over StorageInit,Storage: Flow 4: Storage Initialization
        Note right of StorageInit: Injected as init container<br/>by pod mutating webhook
        StorageInit->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Cloud credentials (IAM/token)
        Storage-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts
        Note right of StorageInit: Write to local filesystem<br/>(emptyDir/PVC)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,ISVC_N: Flow 5: InferenceGraph Multi-Step Pipeline
        Client->>RouterPod: POST inference request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Optional Bearer token
        RouterPod->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>(if auth enabled)
        K8sAPI-->>RouterPod: Authorized
        RouterPod->>PredSvc: Step 1: InferenceService<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Istio mTLS
        PredSvc-->>RouterPod: Step 1 Result
        RouterPod->>ISVC_N: Step N: InferenceService<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Istio mTLS
        ISVC_N-->>RouterPod: Step N Result
        RouterPod-->>Client: Combined Response
    end
